"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-17-katarina-johnson-thompson-im-strong-place-ahead-paris-olympics-21245506\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompsonis in a good place as her fourthOlympicslooms on the horizon and shrugs off her latest injury concerns.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"score\": 0.9999931634039924, \"rank\": 5.934501898976782e-06, \"text\": \"Katarina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A double world champion in the heptathlon, the Liverpudlian has never reached the podium at the Games but feels well placed to challenge inParis.\", \"from\": 130, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 177, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"score\": 0.9969515695454481, \"rank\": 0.0030577517983739998, \"text\": \"Liverpudlian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She suffered an injury scare at June's European Championships, withdrawing after three events with a leg problem, but is in a positive frame of mind.\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4313138727028743e-21, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And despite more than her share of setbacks, including an agonising early exit at the Tokyo Olympics because of injury, the 31-year-old who claimed her second world gold last year tells Metro she would change nothing about her journey.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Manchester was good in parts, those two events have been going really well in training and I wanted to see them put together in a competition environment.\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 665, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"score\": 0.9999999995093276, \"rank\": 2.4165635008232184e-10, \"text\": \"Manchester\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not get the result I wanted in the javelin [finishing ninth with 42.38metres] but I did in the 200m [runner-up toDina Asher-Smithin 23.20 seconds].\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a cold, wet, windy day and I wasn't expecting that much.\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had two goals: I had not run a 200m this year so wanted to get the mark there so that I can be in the final heat in France.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998221119659504, \"rank\": 0.00017488080040944855, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really, really shocked at doing that time in those conditions.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a good weekend overall.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aston has been pivotal.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been able to turn those hard times around, I feel he gives me strength.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really happy with the mindset he has helped me work on.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He reinforces me with facts and is so calm, and so I believe everything he says.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He does not give credit easily, so it means something when he does.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aston has [helped athletes win] so many medals in the sport and his experience is invaluable in that sense.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I never really show fitness or form going into a heptathlon so that's normal for me!\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I put it together every time and it's fine.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as I can get to the startline fit and healthy I always believe I have a real chance.\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not feel I have got unfinished business at the Olympics, I just feel those Olympic experiences have not gone as I wanted them to.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2051, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just want to give myself a really good chance in Paris.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998335625, \"rank\": 1.6666075275276878e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to be able to say wherever I finish in the field that I will have given my best performance.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mentally I let myself down in Rio and it was the opposite in Tokyo where I was in a really good place mentally but not physically.\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999719102566, \"rank\": 2.808977313835379e-08, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6981527295284217, \"rank\": 0.4323511150007434, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing has gone perfectly.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I have gained good experience from every single one I have been to, for example the crowd from 2012 - and I think we will get something similar in Paris - or the pressure that was on me in Rio in 2016.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2530, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998335625, \"rank\": 1.6666075275276878e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999719102566, \"rank\": 2.808977313835379e-08, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I am in a strong place and my body is in a healthy place now.\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now it's about taking it day by day ahead of Paris.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998335625, \"rank\": 1.6666075275276878e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One hundred per cent.\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had a lot of downs in my story as well as the ups but when I look back, I feel lucky.\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have overcome the harder times and then come through that to the other side and won the world title again in Budapest last year.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2940, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.999486657478019, \"rank\": 0.0005136061778537639, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not change a thing about my story.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"British Gas commissioned a mural for me in my home city and it is absolutely incredible.\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3004, \"end\": 3015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"score\": 0.9830961297432252, \"rank\": 0.009499152226353233, \"text\": \"British Gas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the second time I have worked with the artist Paul Curtis, who is a local legend.\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3144, \"end\": 3155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Curtis_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.8775081799577619, \"rank\": 0.13131313131310177, \"text\": \"Paul Curtis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Curtis_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Curtis_(musician)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It says on it 'You will never run alone' as a nod to the team I support, Liverpool.\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.247588119029565e-13, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had a luckier career than most have.\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it does not happen, I have been very fortunate and I do not want people feeling sorry for me.\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will go there and give it my all to get the result I want.\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"British Gas has commissioned a 30-metre mural ofKatarina Johnson-Thompsonfeaturing motivational phrases proven to power positivity, with the aim of supporting the heptathlete and inspiring the local Liverpool community  ArrowMORE:Jessica Ennis-Hill backs Katarina Johnson-Thompson to end Olympic heartache at Paris 2024  ArrowMORE:Happy, relaxed and in love with my diving - why I am a Paris winner whatever the result  ArrowMORE:I am a running world champion but I am not getting excited about the Olympics yet  For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 4029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"score\": 0.9830961297432252, \"rank\": 0.009499152226353233, \"text\": \"British Gas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Gas\"}, {\"begin\": 3667, \"end\": 3676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.247588119029565e-13, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 3698, \"end\": 3716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}, {\"begin\": 3723, \"end\": 3748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 3777, \"end\": 3787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0148565409152206e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3854, \"end\": 3859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998335625, \"rank\": 1.6666075275276878e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4101, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get your favourite puzzles when they are ready to play on the website sent directly to you every day and track your daily streak!\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4384, \"entities\": []}]}"